# AzaLoop Development Rules

Follow the 5-stage pipeline: open → design → build → verify → archive.
Each stage completes its guard checks before advancing.

## Quality Gates
Before marking any story done:
1. TypeScript compilation passes
2. All tests pass
3. Security scan passes (no critical)
4. Acceptance criteria verified

## Session Start
Execute continue.md rules on every session start.
